# Optional: point the control room at a different Battle of Nodes workspace root.
# If omitted, the app assumes this repo sits inside a larger MultiversX workspace
# and resolves artifacts from the parent directory.
BON_WORKSPACE_ROOT=/path/to/your/MultiversX-workspace

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supernova Sprint onchain leaderboard (testnet) -- gasless relayer (/api/relay)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The relayer signing key. Pays TESTNET gas for players' score submissions
# (Relayed v3). TESTNET ONLY -- no real value. Set ONE of the two below as a
# Vercel env var (Production). NEVER commit a real key.
#
# Option A (recommended): the full contents of the relayer PEM file.
#   RELAYER_PEM="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY for erd1...-----\n<base64>\n-----END PRIVATE KEY for erd1...-----"
# Option B: the 64-hex secret key.
#   RELAYER_SECRET_KEY=<64-hex-secret-key>
#
# The key MUST correspond to the relayer address in
# src/lib/onchain/leaderboard.config.ts (RELAYER_ADDRESS), and that wallet must
# be funded with testnet EGLD (faucet). The relayer must be in the same shard as
# the player's ephemeral key (the client grinds the key into the relayer shard;
# the default relayer is in shard 0).
RELAYER_PEM=
# RELAYER_SECRET_KEY=

# Optional overrides (only if you deploy the contract or relayer differently).
# These are PUBLIC (exposed to the browser), so they are NEXT_PUBLIC_*.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_LEADERBOARD_CONTRACT=erd1qqqqqqqqqqqqqpgq...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RELAYER_ADDRESS=erd1...
